title.rendered: Tenby All Weather Aluminium Bar Stool – Various Heights

content.rendered:
The Tenby Bar Stool is made from a gorgeous aluminium frame frame with a faux vintage distressed finish. It comes in a choice of colours and also has sister items specifically designed to work as a set. Finished with a clear lacquer to deter further chipping. Each chair is individually distressed for a unique look! Ideal for indoor or outdoor use!

In stock for delivery in 3-5 working days.

Comes with a 12 month guarantee.

For use indoors and outdoors.
